HEADWORD: Fronde
<hw>Fronde</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <fld>(F.
Hist.)</fld> <def>A political party in France, during the minority of
Louis XIV., who opposed the government, and made war upon the court
party.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

